{
  "text": "For the RT-PCR for the detection of FMDV nucleic acid, the SuperScript III One-Step RT-PCR System with Platinum Taq DNA Polymerase (Invitrogen, Waltham, MA, USA) and primers for the 3D region were used [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "29870371"
